# ACTA documentation sync (product manager rule)

Treat documentation as part of the deliverable. A code change is incomplete until every affected surface below is updated in the same PR.

## Documentation inventory

| Surface | Path | Audience |
|---------|------|----------|
| Root overview | `README.md` | Everyone |
| PM guide | `docs/PM_GUIDE.md` | PMs, partners |
| Architecture | `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` | Engineers, auditors |
| Protocol flow | `docs/FLOW.md` | Engineers |
| API reference | `docs/API_REFERENCE.md` | Integrators |
| Normative spec | `docs/SPEC.md` | Spec readers |
| Roadmap | `docs/ROADMAP.md` | Everyone |
| Security audit | `docs/SECURITY_AUDIT.md` | Engineers, auditors |
| ADRs | `docs/adr/*.md` | Engineers |
| Mermaid diagrams | `docs/diagrams/*.mermaid` | Engineers |
| Standalone diagram | `docs/protocol-diagram.html` | Presentations |
| OpenAC SDK | `openac-sdk/README.md` | SDK users |
| `@acta/sdk` | `packages/sdk/README.md` | Integrators |
